        "function_call": {
          "id": null,
          "args": {
            "command": "cat << 'EOF' > docs/API_CONTRACTS.md\n# API Contracts: Dimensional Factor Pulse (DFP)\n\n## > BEGIN_ENVIRONMENT\nStack: React/Vite (pnpm), Python (uv), PostgreSQL, Docker Compose\nEntry_Point: http://localhost:8000\nInterface_Mount_Selector: #root\nINTEGRATION_TEST_CMD: CI=true npx playwright test --reporter=list\n## > END_ENVIRONMENT\n\n## > BEGIN_MODULE: ui-gateway\nType: ORCHESTRATOR\nDescription: React/Vite frontend served by Nginx, acting as a reverse proxy to the backend API. Responsible for global docker-compose.yml orchestration.\n\n### Routing Contract\n- **Nginx Routing**: \n  - `/` -> Serves static React assets.\n  - `/api/` -> Reverse proxies to `http://logic-api:8001/api/`.\n- **Docker Compose Orchestration**:\n  - Service `ui-gateway`: Builds React app, serves via Nginx. Maps host port 8000 to container port 80.\n  - Service `logic-api`: Builds Python app. Maps host port 8001 to container port 8001.\n  - Service `data-store`: PostgreSQL database. Internal network only.\n\n### UI Components & Controls\n- **Framework**: React/Vite (pnpm), Tailwind CSS.\n- **Visualization**: `@nivo/heatmap` (X-axis: date, Y-axis: funds, Color: positive/negative premium).\n- **Fund Selector**: Dropdown for proxy pairs:\n  - US Core Equity: DFAC vs ^GSPC\n  - Intl. Vector: DXIV vs URTH\n  - Emerging Markets: DFAE vs EEM\n- **Timeframe Toggle**: Buttons for 1D, 5D, 1M, 6M, 1Y, YTD.\n- **Metadata Footer**: Displays \"Built by SDLC-Factory\", automated build timestamp, and git hash.\n- **UX Requirements**: Descriptive metric names, interactive heatmap with clear color differentiation, legend, vertical text for narrow columns, and tooltip on hover (date, premium value, region, proxy pair).\n\n### Data Consumption\n- Fetches data from `/api/data?fund_id=<string>&timeframe=<string>`.\n- Expects strict JSON response matching Nivo heatmap format:\n  `[ { \"id\": string, \"data\": [ { \"x\": string, \"y\": number } ] } ]`\n## > END_MODULE: ui-gateway\n\n## > BEGIN_MODULE: logic-api\nType: LEAF\nDescription: Python backend API managed by `uv`, responsible for fetching financial data, calculating factor premiums, and serving the frontend.\n\n### Initialization & Resilience\n- **Database Polling**: Must implement a polling loop (e.g., `tenacity`) to wait for `data-store` (up to 10 attempts, 2 seconds apart) before seeding or binding the port.\n- **Data Seeding**: On first boot, fetch the last 730 days of data for DFAC, ^GSPC, DXIV, URTH, DFAE, EEM using `yfinance` and store in `data-store`.\n\n### Calculation Logic\n- **Premium Calculation**: Premium = DFA Proxy Return - Benchmark Return.\n- **Precision**: Calculated and stored to 4 decimal places.\n\n### Endpoints\n- **`GET /health`**\n  - Returns: `{ \"status\": \"string\", \"db_connected\": boolean }`\n- **`GET /api/data`**\n  - Query Parameters: \n    - `fund_id` (string): e.g., \"US Core Equity\", \"Intl. Vector\", \"Emerging Markets\"\n    - `timeframe` (string): \"1D\", \"5D\", \"1M\", \"6M\", \"1Y\", \"YTD\"\n  - Returns strict JSON (Nivo heatmap format):\n    `[ { \"id\": \"US Core Equity\", \"data\": [ { \"x\": \"2023-10-01\", \"y\": 0.0123 } ] } ]`\n\n### Environment\n- **Port**: Binds to 8001 internally.\n## > END_MODULE: logic-api\n\n## > BEGIN_MODULE: data-store\nType: LEAF\nDescription: PostgreSQL database for caching daily adjusted market closes and calculated premiums.\n\n### Schema Contract\n- **Table**: `market_closes`\n  - `date` (DATE)\n  - `ticker` (VARCHAR)\n  - `adj_close` (NUMERIC)\n  - PRIMARY KEY (`date`, `ticker`)\n- **Table**: `premiums`\n  - `date` (DATE)\n  - `fund_id` (VARCHAR)\n  - `premium` (NUMERIC(10, 4))\n  - PRIMARY KEY (`date`, `fund_id`)\n\n### Infrastructure\n- **Persistence**: Docker volumes.\n- **Network**: Internal network access only (unreachable from host).\n- **Credentials**: Configured via environment variables.\n## > END_MODULE: data-store\nEOF"
          },
